I"I<p>The <a href="/documentation/elements/tag/">tag</a> is a small but useful element that can be used in many contexts, to <strong>enhance</strong> the meaning of the text itâ€™s attached to.</p>

<p>A tag rarely comes on its own though, so Bulma now supports <a href="/documentation/elements/tag/#list-of-tags">list of tags</a>. The same way you can <a href="together">group controls</a>, you can now <strong>group tags together</strong> to form a list that can span multiple lines.</p>

